Let's get connected!

I like to meet new people. And so far, I have been working on my own. I would like to change that someday.

Regarding coding and in general, I get really inspired by seeing how experienced people code, surf or think. Besides that, I think there are only few things as interesting as getting to know sombody else's point of view.

Feel free to contact me. I would like to listen to your feedback on this game and to hear about your projects. Just send me a request via LinkedIn or Xing and let's communicate about coding, projects and the world.
